          <h2 id="what-is-geometry-dash">What is Geometry Dash?</h2>
          <p>Geometry Dash is a <a href="/c/rhythm-games/">rhythm-based platformer</a> game that has captivated millions of players worldwide. Created by <a href="https://twitter.com/RobTopGames" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Robert Topala (RobTop Games)</a> and released in 2013, this game combines the simplicity of one-button controls with the complexity of challenging level design. The core mechanic is straightforward: tap to jump, but the execution requires precision timing, pattern recognition, and musical synchronization. You can download the official game from the <a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/geometry-dash/id625334537" target="_blank" rel="noopener">App Store</a> or <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.robtopx.geometryjump" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play</a>.</p>

