          <h2 id="faq">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

          <h3>Is Geometry Dash really free?</h3>
          <p>Yes, Geometry Dash is completely free to play on geometrydash.ie. There are no hidden costs, no in-app purchases required, and no ads interrupting gameplay. Simply open your browser and start playing instantly.</p>

